    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Presenting a truly exceptional vehicle that stands as a testament to meticulous ownership. This car is in showroom condition, having been fastidiously maintained in a climate-controlled garage since day one. The exterior paint retains a deep, mirror-like luster with absolutely no stone chips, scratches, or swirl marks, while the alloy wheels are pristine without a hint of curb rash. Inside, the cabin is a time capsule; the premium leather remains supple with zero bolster wear, and the 'new car' scent is still subtly present. Every electronic feature and driver-assist system functions flawlessly. Mechanically, the car is beyond reproach, boasting a full service history exclusively through authorized technicians. It has never seen rain or snow, and the undercarriage is as clean as the bodywork. This is not just a used car; it is a collector-quality example that drives with the same tightness and precision as it did the day it rolled off the assembly line.",
      "price": 48500.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
